{"tid":2124913,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"Midnight Gospel ❍ 午夜福音討論區","createTime":"2020-07-25T19:03:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T12:57:39.000Z","uid":91753,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"120cf537840a76d6a24c98d518477fd37d10d36d","tid":2124913,"uid":91753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T19:03:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zMts5sD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzMts5sD.png&h=4075d0cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食用指南：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 應該點睇？<br />\n<br />\n一集最少睇三次，一次係就咁睇，第二次係就人咁聽內容，唔好睇畫面，因為成套嘢就係一個mindfulness training，合上眼，集中精神喺對談，係好好嘅了解方法。<br />\n<br />\n第三次睇，大概會明白多啲。喺外國嘅歡迎加料服用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.佢講嘅嘢我聽唔明，點算？<br />\n<br />\n你可以試吓去Google當中你有興趣嘅字眼，每一隻重點字眼已經可以打開你新世界嘅大門， 願眼睛指引你。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但亦都好歡迎就咁當佢係動畫片咁睇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 「屌你班神秘撚，成班都痴撚線，講埋啲鳩嘢，入青山啦，睇睇睇睇你老母呀？」<br />\n<br />\n連登仔對不起我傷害了你請原諒我對你造成的傷害謝謝你之前所做的一切我愛你一直都愛著你願原力與你同在。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4jecw8X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4jecw8X.jpg&h=ad103c76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n靈感同大腦未連繄完整，拋磚引玉。<br />\n<br />\n個人最中意ep3 ep5，係elixir 一樣嘅soul medicine ，好好嘅lesson to remind us what/who/where/which node we are  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&middot; 第五集<br />\n<br />\n露魂之旅嘅過程<br />\n<br />\n業力法則流動<br />\n<br />\n真正揚升方法<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d5kSw7L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd5kSw7L.jpg&h=42f27dad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&middot; 第三集<br />\n<br />\nMagick 中across the abyss 嘅過程<br />\n<br />\n「印心」嘅重要性<br />\n<br />\nMagus 未完全降服ego 時，了悟後會出現嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SXD8PVp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSXD8PVp.png&h=9500bf6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有請連登法師們<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"115532bab8acee0ba2473fcbb1a9f35842acbf51","tid":2124913,"uid":78390,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T20:26:02.000Z","msg":"最尾個三集我LSD睇<br />\n<br />\n同啊媽傾計個集好又感觸 好似feel到分娩嘅痛楚 生命係一種好強大嘅能量<br />\n<br />\n巴打個po 擺去影視台應該多啲人留意"},{"pid":"f2e77bd86fe64bd8adf9439bab57212048357003","tid":2124913,"uid":91753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"115532bab8acee0ba2473fcbb1a9f35842acbf51","tid":2124913,"uid":78390,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T20:26:02.000Z","msg":"最尾個三集我LSD睇<br />\n<br />\n同啊媽傾計個集好又感觸 好似feel到分娩嘅痛楚 生命係一種好強大嘅能量<br />\n<br />\n巴打個po 擺去影視台應該多啲人留意"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T11:20:17.000Z","msg":"多謝你<br />\n我去影視台開先<br />\n<br />\nL嗰時connect咗去邊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe91e12cfbc6ca9aa94560e03e05fcd356be89a3","tid":2124913,"uid":105815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T16:37:38.000Z","msg":"其實畫面show 嘅野同佢地傾嘅野係咪冇關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f09afb6a57a8169d242c4cb065b23d266e88913c","tid":2124913,"uid":91753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe91e12cfbc6ca9aa94560e03e05fcd356be89a3","tid":2124913,"uid":105815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T16:37:38.000Z","msg":"其實畫面show 嘅野同佢地傾嘅野係咪冇關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T17:54:58.000Z","msg":"唔關事㗎，對話係由Podcast剪出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4082a733ea9a02dd8b93ca23248eda4f5392517a","tid":2124913,"uid":91753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quot